---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Fashion & Apparel Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/ecommerce-retail/fashion-apparel" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Fashion & Apparel
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Fashion</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">13 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Fashion & Apparel Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Build hype for launches, recover abandoned carts, and create VIP customers who shop every season.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Fashion is fast-paced and competitive. The brands that win are those that build anticipation, personalize the experience, and reward loyalty.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Building Launch Hype</h2>

          <p>
            Every collection launch is an opportunity to create urgency. Waitlists build anticipation and give VIPs exclusive early access.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">The Launch Sequence</h3>

          <div class="bg-pink-50 p-6 rounded-xl my-6">
            <ol class="space-y-3 mb-0">
              <li><strong>2 weeks out:</strong> Coming soon announcement with waitlist</li>
              <li><strong>1 week out:</strong> Sneak peek to waitlist members</li>
              <li><strong>24 hours:</strong> VIP early access opens</li>
              <li><strong>Launch day:</strong> General access with urgency messaging</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Fashion Cart Recovery</h2>

          <p>
            Fashion has the highest cart abandonment rate of any category. Multi-step recovery with product images brings shoppers back.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">VIP Loyalty Programs</h2>

          <p>
            Tiered loyalty programs reward your best customers and incentivize higher spending. VIPs get early access, exclusive sales, and personalized service.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 to-rose-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your Fashion Brand?</h3>
            <p class="text-pink-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your brand.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-pink-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
